text: Kanly () is a rural locality (a selo) in Akhmetovsky Selsoviet, Kushnarenkovsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 208 as of 2010. There are 3 streets. == Geography == It is located 21 km from Kushnarenkovo, 3 km from Akhmetovo. == References == Category:Rural localities in Kushnarenkovsky District
title: Kanly, Kushnarenkovsky District, Republic of Bashkortostan
